										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The week of an issue release is always an exciting one! Have you read <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/issue/issue-050/">Issue 050</a> yet? It has 18 stellar stories to keep you occupied, and if that&#8217;s just not enough LSQ for you, we have even more content down below:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-27745" src="https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ian-schneider-PAykYb-8Er8-unsplash-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" srcset="https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ian-schneider-PAykYb-8Er8-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ian-schneider-PAykYb-8Er8-unsplash-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ian-schneider-PAykYb-8Er8-unsplash-768x513.jpg 768w, https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ian-schneider-PAykYb-8Er8-unsplash-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ian-schneider-PAykYb-8Er8-unsplash-2048x1367.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<ul>
<li>On <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/modern-day-sirens-amethyst-kiah/"><strong>Monday</strong></a>, K. Hartless introduced us to Amethyst Kiah, a queer Black musician with her own unique sound;</li>
<li>On <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/issue-050-release-meet-cover-artist-theodora-capat/"><strong>Wednesday</strong></a>, we had the pleasure of interviewing Theodora Capat, this issue&#8217;s fabulous cover artist;</li>
<li>On <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/love-letter-2/"><strong>Thursday</strong></a>, Liza Wemakor shared reflections on love;</li>
<li>On <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/review-escape-the-field/"><strong>Friday</strong></a>, Eve Taft reviewed the corn maze horror movie <em>Escape the Field</em>.</li>
</ul>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
