										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Don&#8217;t head into the weekend without some of our quality blog posts to keep you company! Here&#8217;s a roundup of our latest batch:</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-27490" src="https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/arr-n-K4Ax6MhyYSk-unsplash-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/arr-n-K4Ax6MhyYSk-unsplash-300x225.jpg 300w, https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/arr-n-K4Ax6MhyYSk-unsplash-1024x769.jpg 1024w, https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/arr-n-K4Ax6MhyYSk-unsplash-768x577.jpg 768w, https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/arr-n-K4Ax6MhyYSk-unsplash-1536x1153.jpg 1536w, https://lunastationquarterly.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/arr-n-K4Ax6MhyYSk-unsplash-2048x1538.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<ul>
<li>On <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/lsq-monthly-news-flash-may-2022/"><strong>Monday</strong></a>, we shared our news for the month of May;</li>
<li>On <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/issue-049-author-interview-ivy-grimes-and-the-goddess-of-fear/"><strong>Tuesday</strong></a>, we talked to <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/issue/issue-049/">Issue 049</a> author Ivy Grimes about revisions and her story &#8220;<a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/story/the-goddess-of-fear/">The Goddess of Fear</a>&#8220;;</li>
<li>On <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/review-the-memory-librarian-2022/"><strong>Wednesday</strong></a>, Liza Wemakor shared her thorough review of Janelle Monae&#8217;s sci-fi anthology <em>The Memory Librarian</em>;</li>
<li>On <a href="https://lunastationquarterly.com/scares-of-all-shapes-and-sizes-categorizing-fear/"><strong>Thursday</strong></a>, Eve Taft explored the different categories of fear;</li>
